HEADWORD: Chrysalis
<hw>Chrys"a*lis</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Chrysalides</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[L.
<ets>chrysallis</ets> the gold-colored pupa of butterflies, Gr. <?/, fr.
<?/ gold. Cf. <er>Aurelia</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The pupa
